PrecisAcceptance of an instrument (Revocation of Surrender) duly approved by the members of the TSUU T'INA NATION BAND OF INDIANS which provides for the partial revocation of a 1974 surrender so that a parcel of land (60.6 hectares) situated on Sarcee Indian Reserve No. 145 in Alberta which had been surrendered for leasing to third party interests can be returned to reserve status. (Lot 11, C.L.S.R. Plan 67856)
